title: KB Covers Ultra Clear Mac Keyboard CLEARSKINMUS Features
description:
KB Covers Ultra Clear Mac Keyboard Skin - CLEARSKINMUS - http://www.abt.com/product/64740/KB-Covers-CLEARSKINMUS.html  

Designed to protect from dust dirt and spills the ClearSkin keyboard cover has been perfectly engineered to fit your MacBook MacBook Air or MacBook Pro (Unibody)...and allow the backlit keys to shine through. The ClearSkin keyboard cover is the thinnest clearest cover we have ever made.
And now it also fits the Apple Ultra-Thin Wireless Keyboard!
The ClearSkin keyboard cover is made of a 0.1mm advanced space-age plastic so clear that it is almost invisible when put on the keyboard...and because it is so thin you can hardly notice it when typing.
Features:
• Hand washable and easy to keep clean.
